00:16:14.100 --> 00:16:15.400
&gt;&gt; Speaker 1: What
was your inspiration

00:16:15.400 --> 00:16:18.090
for the main character's friend?

00:16:18.090 --> 00:16:19.390
&gt;&gt; Jennifer A Nielsen: Oh.

00:16:19.390 --> 00:16:21.280
Okay. So "Night Divided"
is the --

00:16:21.280 --> 00:16:24.120
is a Berlin Wall escape story.

00:16:24.120 --> 00:16:26.520
The main character is Gerta.

00:16:26.520 --> 00:16:30.200
Her friend is Anna.

00:16:30.200 --> 00:16:32.050
To understand Anna, you have

00:16:32.050 --> 00:16:36.790
to understand what East
Germany was like in 1964.

00:16:36.790 --> 00:16:39.310
This is the best way
to understand it.

00:16:39.310 --> 00:16:42.710
At the height of its
power, the secret police

00:16:42.710 --> 00:16:46.130
and the Soviet Union,
that was the KGB,

00:16:46.130 --> 00:16:51.590
they had one secret agent
for every 5,600 citizens.

00:16:51.590 --> 00:16:55.510
So every 5,600 people,
1 secret police.

00:16:55.510 --> 00:16:57.690
At the height of the
power for the Gestapo.

00:16:57.690 --> 00:17:00.620
That's the secret
police of the Nazis.

00:17:00.620 --> 00:17:04.330
1 secret policeman
for 2,000 citizens.

00:17:04.330 --> 00:17:11.180
In 1964 the secret
police were the Stasi.

00:17:11.180 --> 00:17:18.120
They had 1 secret police
for every 166 individuals.

00:17:18.120 --> 00:17:19.820
But that wasn't good
enough for them.

00:17:19.820 --> 00:17:22.430
Every apartment building
has a spy.

00:17:22.430 --> 00:17:24.660
Your bus driver was
probably a spy.

00:17:24.660 --> 00:17:25.980
Your postman was a spy.

00:17:25.980 --> 00:17:27.820
Your teacher was a spy.

00:17:27.820 --> 00:17:32.420
And then Anna, her best friend
in the story, became recruited.

00:17:32.420 --> 00:17:36.260
Right? If you take the total
number of spies and informants

00:17:36.260 --> 00:17:40.890
that the Stasi used, the number
went to 1 in 12 which means,

00:17:40.890 --> 00:17:46.340
in this room, every
section of the carpet,

00:17:46.340 --> 00:17:49.450
every row in this
room, at least 1 person

00:17:49.450 --> 00:17:54.020
on that row would be
here to spy on you.

00:17:54.020 --> 00:17:56.430
Anna is there as a best friend

00:17:56.430 --> 00:18:00.510
because she was positively
representing that part

00:18:00.510 --> 00:18:03.690
of East Germany which
means trust no one

00:18:03.690 --> 00:18:05.940
because you could
not trust anyone.

00:18:05.940 --> 00:18:09.650
That was an awesome question.

