For an author, stories
will come to you.

00:21:50.710 --> 00:21:52.010
All right?

00:21:52.010 --> 00:21:53.330
I don't necessarily
go looking for them.

00:21:53.330 --> 00:21:54.630
But I know.

00:21:54.630 --> 00:21:57.500
And I -- Do you ever
write stories?

00:21:57.500 --> 00:21:58.800
All right.

00:21:58.800 --> 00:22:00.750
Do you ever get an idea,
and all of a sudden it feels

00:22:00.750 --> 00:22:02.720
like there's magic in your head?

00:22:02.720 --> 00:22:04.420
You know what I'm talking about?

