00:22:12.280 --> 00:22:14.220
about this part of the world.

00:22:14.220 --> 00:22:16.270
I just look for when
I feel magic

00:22:16.270 --> 00:22:18.050
in my head, and I
start to write.

00:22:18.050 --> 00:22:20.420
Same as you.

00:22:20.420 --> 00:22:21.720
Wonderful.

00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:23.020
Wonderful.

